    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>salad </strong>to a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> and gently mix together – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Pat your <strong>rump steak[s]</strong> dry with kitchen paper, then drizzle with <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> on both sides</p>",
