    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>rested steak[s] </strong>finely</p><p>Divide the <strong>balsamic</strong> <strong>onions</strong> between the<strong> toasted ciabatta halves</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> sliced</strong> <strong>steak</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>mustard</strong> <strong>mayo </strong>– this is your <strong>open steak sandwich with balsamic onions</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>salad</strong> to the side and sprinkle the <strong>rosemary salt </strong>all over the chips</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
